---

## ğŸŒ API (Open-Meteo)
This project uses two endpoints:

### 1) Geocoding (city search)
`https://geocoding-api.open-meteo.com/v1/search?name={CITY}&count=1&language=en&format=json`

Returns coordinates: `latitude`, `longitude`.

### 2) Forecast (weather by coordinates)
`https://api.open-meteo.com/v1/forecast?latitude={LAT}&longitude={LON}&current=...&daily=...&forecast_days=3&temperature_unit={celsius|fahrenheit}&timezone=auto`

Returns current weather (`current`) and forecast (`daily`).

