## ğŸ“ Project Structure (key files)
- `__assikApp.swift` / `WeatherApp.swift` â€” app entry point (**Important: only one file should contain `@main`**)
- `ContentView.swift` â€” main screen (search + results)
- `SettingsView.swift` â€” settings screen (Â°C/Â°F)
- `Models.swift` â€” `Codable` API models
- `WeatherAPI.swift` â€” networking layer (geocoding + forecast)
