- `WeatherCache.swift` â€” cache storage in `UserDefaults`
- `WeatherViewModel.swift` â€” UI state + calls to repository
- `WeatherCodeMapper.swift` â€” weather code â†’ readable description
- `WeatherCardView.swift` â€” UI card for current weather + forecast

